about a particular type of newspaper, the tabloid.

00:00:34.450 --> 00:00:40.460
It’s a form of small, concise newspaper famous for gossip and sensational stories, but

00:00:40.509 --> 00:00:45.810
this type of newspaper has gone on to become the dominant form of journalism in Britain.

00:00:46.339 --> 00:00:51.663
So, in this exploration of tabloids, and of tabloid culture, we’ll look at how it all

00:00:51.673 --> 00:00:57.283
started, who some of the key players are, the types of stories they write, the controversies

